{pstd}
向聚类分析添加备注

{p 8 22 2}{cmd:cluster} {cmdab:note:s} {it:clname} {cmd::} {it:text}


{pstd}
列出所有聚类备注

{p 8 22 2}{cmd:cluster} {cmdab:note:s}


{pstd}
列出与指定聚类分析相关的备注

{p 8 22 2}{cmd:cluster} {cmdab:note:s} {it:clnamelist}


{pstd}
删除聚类备注

{p 8 22 2}{cmd:cluster} {cmdab:note:s} {cmd:drop} {it:clname}
		[{cmd:in} {it:{help numlist_zh}}]
{p_end}